48:44.679 --> 48:45.679
Here you go.

49:11.539 --> 49:12.750
(100 dollars)

49:40.320 --> 49:42.360
I already told you everything.

49:43.110 --> 49:46.949
I parked my car there to rest for a moment.

49:53.460 --> 50:00.050
(35R 30180)

50:19.440 --> 50:21.280
But I'm not a suspect.

50:21.690 --> 50:22.989
I'm a witness.

50:30.989 --> 50:33.250
Must you be so heartless?

50:34.289 --> 50:37.289
Help a brother out, will you?

50:37.789 --> 50:40.959
Why are you on my case when the trial is over?

50:40.960 --> 50:45.009
As Yoon Hyo Jung's stalker, you must've seen something.

50:45.010 --> 50:46.928
Any man Hong Guk Hwa was seeing...

50:46.929 --> 50:49.718
or someone who had a reason to kill her.

50:49.719 --> 50:52.139
How could I possibly know that?

50:52.429 --> 50:54.809
She got around, you know.

50:56.769 --> 50:58.940
You must've seen the photo too.

51:03.239 --> 51:04.239
What photo?

51:06.150 --> 51:07.159
Or maybe you didn't.

51:08.659 --> 51:10.239
During the investigation that led to a fine,

51:10.699 --> 51:12.489
the police confiscated all the photos I took.

51:15.119 --> 51:16.119
Really?

51:47.570 --> 51:50.489
- Jeez. - Hey, check him out.

51:53.369 --> 51:54.369
(There's a light at the end of the tunnel.)

52:11.969 --> 52:17.889
(Self-realization, Character Building)

52:31.320 --> 52:37.250
(Advanced Correctional Practice for a Better Tomorrow)

52:54.639 --> 52:56.849
This really is the last time, okay?

52:57.599 --> 52:59.519
My heart is still racing.

52:59.889 --> 53:01.768
It hurts.

53:01.769 --> 53:03.440
Don't be ridiculous.

53:04.480 --> 53:07.650
Hey, how about now? Does it still hurt?

53:09.650 --> 53:11.909
My gosh, this is a lot.

53:12.820 --> 53:15.530
You see, I understand why you're doing this,

53:16.159 --> 53:18.699
but you need to know when to stop.

53:19.579 --> 53:20.659
Thank you.

53:21.250 --> 53:22.289
I'm off.

53:41.599 --> 53:43.649
(Yoo Seung Hoon, Evidence 1)

53:43.650 --> 53:44.730
(Chungang Police Station, Digital Evidence)

53:49.860 --> 53:51.569
(October 13, 2020)

53:51.570 --> 53:53.489
(October 27, 2020)

53:53.570 --> 53:54.909
(February 17, 2021)

53:54.989 --> 53:57.909
(March 30 - 31, 2021)

54:18.760 --> 54:26.769
(Call History)

54:32.690 --> 54:35.449
(Call History)

54:38.239 --> 54:39.329
Okay.

55:02.469 --> 55:07.018
(Alcoholism Treatment)

55:07.019 --> 55:08.019
Hello?

55:09.400 --> 55:10.400
Hello?

55:12.570 --> 55:13.820
What was that?

55:15.449 --> 55:18.949
She was prescribed fentanyl six months ago.

55:19.119 --> 55:21.699
At the time, it wasn't classified as a narcotic.

55:22.579 --> 55:25.539
(Call History, March 30 - 31, 2021)

55:35.420 --> 55:36.880
So it was you?

55:39.389 --> 55:44.679
(Alcoholism Treatment)

55:55.860 --> 55:57.238
Grandpa!

55:57.239 --> 55:58.489
Yes!

55:59.239 --> 56:01.738
My sweet pumpkin. Did you have fun?

56:01.739 --> 56:02.739
Yes.

56:03.289 --> 56:05.159
Here, do you want one?

56:06.500 --> 56:09.039
- Go have some more fun. - Okay.

56:12.840 --> 56:14.210
Oh, boy.

56:19.800 --> 56:21.010
My gosh.

56:22.300 --> 56:23.349
How adorable.

56:24.849 --> 56:26.059
What's going on?

56:41.780 --> 56:45.199
Doctor Park Chan Yeol had an affair with Hong Guk Hwa.

56:46.579 --> 56:49.369
Upon finding out that he was a married man,

56:49.619 --> 56:51.250
she wanted to end things with him.

57:03.679 --> 57:05.010
It's too late.

57:05.889 --> 57:07.469
There's nothing I can do now.

57:10.230 --> 57:12.150
- Grandpa! - Yes.

57:13.650 --> 57:16.019
- Was that fun? - Yes.

57:18.360 --> 57:22.530
Every parent loves their children as much as you cherish your own.

57:23.699 --> 57:26.159
You sent an innocent guy to jail.

57:26.869 --> 57:28.829
How can you live with yourself after what you did?

57:36.550 --> 57:39.210
Well, do whatever you want.

57:39.300 --> 57:42.050
- Bye, kiddo. - Bye.

57:51.429 --> 57:53.559
(Call History)

58:03.409 --> 58:06.869
I'm sorry I can't tie up loose ends myself when I started this,

58:08.449 --> 58:09.579
but Park Chan Yeol...

58:11.659 --> 58:13.539
I think we should bring him in for an interview.

58:14.170 --> 58:17.340
(An Tae Hee)

59:04.469 --> 59:05.800
Inmate 7927.

59:07.639 --> 59:09.099
Inmate 7927!

59:12.889 --> 59:13.929
You have a visitor.

59:14.139 --> 59:17.809
(Advanced Correctional Practice for a Better Tomorrow)

59:23.530 --> 59:28.110
(Order)

59:55.429 --> 59:56.639
What brings you here?

1:00:01.900 --> 1:00:04.570
I don't know where to start.

1:00:09.280 --> 1:00:10.780
The killer has been caught.

1:00:12.409 --> 1:00:14.329
He has admitted to everything.

1:00:18.079 --> 1:00:19.670
His name is Park Chan Yeol.

1:00:21.170 --> 1:00:24.750
The doctor who prescribed fentanyl to Guk Hwa. He killed her.

1:00:28.429 --> 1:00:31.849
You can get out of here now, Hyun Soo.

1:00:33.389 --> 1:00:34.719
You're free.

1:00:43.730 --> 1:00:45.150
You see,

1:00:47.150 --> 1:00:49.199
both the police and the prosecution...

1:00:50.570 --> 1:00:52.118
needed to pin it on someone.

1:00:52.119 --> 1:00:53.659
And there are times when they frame an innocent person.

1:00:55.119 --> 1:00:57.869
Yes, that's just how...

1:00:58.579 --> 1:00:59.750
the judicial system works.

1:01:01.250 --> 1:01:02.960
It's how justice...

1:01:03.960 --> 1:01:05.090
Justice...

1:01:05.960 --> 1:01:07.090
Never mind.

1:01:09.469 --> 1:01:12.010
Too bad you crossed paths with a third-rate lawyer like me.

1:01:13.389 --> 1:01:15.510
Just blame it on bad luck.

1:01:19.179 --> 1:01:20.389
I'm sorry.

1:01:24.309 --> 1:01:25.650
In any case,

1:01:27.860 --> 1:01:29.820
you stayed strong and held out.

1:01:33.320 --> 1:01:34.619
You did well.

1:01:58.010 --> 1:01:59.179
Mr. Shin.

1:02:07.940 --> 1:02:09.320
Thank you for everything.

1:02:17.239 --> 1:02:18.449
Yes, I know.

1:02:23.869 --> 1:02:27.460
(Order)

1:02:29.800 --> 1:02:31.920
The prosecution arrested and indicted Kim Hyun Soo...

1:02:32.340 --> 1:02:35.590
as the prime suspect of the murder on the day of the incident.

1:02:36.090 --> 1:02:39.599
Kim Hyun Soo was founded guilty based on the sufficient evidence,

1:02:39.929 --> 1:02:42.058
witness testimonies, and reasonable arguments...

1:02:42.059 --> 1:02:45.019
presented during the trials.

1:02:45.900 --> 1:02:47.610
However, he had consistently insisted...

1:02:48.480 --> 1:02:51.820
that he was innocent, and parts of his claim...

1:02:51.940 --> 1:02:53.449
appeared to be true,

1:02:53.780 --> 1:02:56.569
so for the sake of judicial justice,

1:02:56.570 --> 1:02:59.279
we tracked down and investigated additional suspects...

1:02:59.280 --> 1:03:01.868
and ended up catching the real killer,

1:03:01.869 --> 1:03:03.659
who has now confessed to the crime.

1:03:04.409 --> 1:03:07.328
This was achieved through the joint investigation...

1:03:07.329 --> 1:03:09.920
of the police and the prosecution who did not give up...

1:03:10.090 --> 1:03:12.920
and persevered until the real culprit was caught.

1:03:13.630 --> 1:03:15.630
The killer deliberately destroyed the crime scene...

1:03:15.880 --> 1:03:19.010
in order to throw the police and the prosecution off the track...

1:03:30.769 --> 1:03:32.110
Inmate 7927.

1:04:24.289 --> 1:04:26.289
(Ministry of Justice)

1:04:38.929 --> 1:04:42.849
(Northern Prison)

1:05:14.920 --> 1:05:16.960
- Hyun Soo. - Hyun Soo!

1:05:29.980 --> 1:05:33.190
Hyun Soo, you went through so much.

1:05:34.690 --> 1:05:36.530
You did well.

1:05:37.650 --> 1:05:40.030
Come on. Let's go home.

1:05:54.000 --> 1:05:56.090
(Private Taxi)

1:06:18.530 --> 1:06:21.488
All right. It's kimchi stew, Hyun Soo's favourite.

1:06:21.489 --> 1:06:24.359
Good. Now, let's eat.

1:06:24.360 --> 1:06:26.869
Goodness. Let me get you some.

1:06:36.420 --> 1:06:39.629
Honey, you should've at least grilled him some meat.

1:06:39.630 --> 1:06:40.880
This is hardly a feast.

1:06:41.760 --> 1:06:46.969
My gosh, you're right. I've been so out of it lately.

1:06:47.349 --> 1:06:49.969
This is still a feast, right?

1:06:50.469 --> 1:06:52.519
Let's eat. Hyun Soo, eat up.

1:06:52.639 --> 1:06:53.769
Enjoy.

1:06:54.480 --> 1:06:56.349
All right.

1:07:02.860 --> 1:07:04.400
I like your new haircut.

1:07:04.780 --> 1:07:05.780
It suits you.

