Remain silent. Just don't say a word.

1:13:32.630 --> 1:13:34.000
That's right.

1:13:38.170 --> 1:13:39.630
Darn it.

1:13:46.260 --> 1:13:48.180
(Chungang Police Station)

1:13:53.479 --> 1:13:55.399
Lose some weight, will you?

1:13:55.569 --> 1:13:56.569
Whatever.

1:13:58.739 --> 1:14:00.028
(Information and Reception)

1:14:00.029 --> 1:14:01.029
Hey.

1:14:01.030 --> 1:14:02.359
(Holding Cells)

1:14:04.409 --> 1:14:05.409
Thanks.

1:14:09.789 --> 1:14:12.289
- Are you Mr. Lee? - That's right.

1:14:14.420 --> 1:14:16.800
- I'm Shin Joong Han. - Right.

1:14:16.840 --> 1:14:20.129
I handled everything with the other lawyer,

1:14:20.130 --> 1:14:21.219
so you may leave.

1:14:21.220 --> 1:14:24.179
It turns out that both parties were responsible in a way.

1:14:24.180 --> 1:14:26.220
